platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: You’ll have to learn through failure
爽快感あふれるアクションゲーム

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: In this entrancing game of skill and spatial awareness, you lob spheres to clear a path through abstract environments, tapping into our innate fascination of watching virtual objects crumble apart. Part reflex challenge, part hypnotic journey across a strange, striking landscape, Smash Hit is a riveting experience.
